textAfterTable: Detailed description   Download .zip .tar.gz   This is a jQuery plugin to turn lists into collapsible trees. It can traverse a given page element and find unordered list elements to turn make them collapse and open when the user clicks the list items. The plugin uses CSS styles to switch the presentation and collapsed state of the list.
